{"tid":1016784,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賺錢搵飯食 - 狼隊 vs 找卡數","createTime":"2019-02-11T03:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T10:40:11.000Z","uid":182056,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bceb0856645ba8ff75e5e87b388edfed32ea9531","tid":1016784,"uid":182056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:38:39.000Z","msg":"狼隊呢排唔知咩事近五場五勝一和入 15 球 ，場均入三球成績好似強隊一樣，馬會讓球開到半一俾狼隊，信心十足咁，貌似贏硬咁款。再睇下找卡數，英超成績差已輸 13 場排在 17 位快要護級，再留意其實咁多隊下游球隊，佢失球數字係最少的 (33 球)，再睇番佢作客輸的都係輸俾前六球隊而已，除了俾利物浦被數四球，佢都係僅僅輸一球俾雙曼和熱刺，面對中下游都可以守和甚至贏波，每次作客受讓都只輸過一次盤，就好似幾年前荷甲隊維迪斯咁，主場輸盤作客贏盤格；狼隊係唔係真係咁勁可以值得 1.62 主勝？今日會留意番佢讓球走勢，如 keep 住半一高水，我係買下盤，如轉盤去到一球就加注。<br />\n<br />\n結輪：睇好找卡數下盤"},{"pid":"e4c930b7e821c669a13f74b8967211a22c7f432d","tid":1016784,"uid":31089,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T06:49:28.000Z","msg":"近五場 五勝一和?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6a6bf9eb2aa457689a3c3ed3e98cff35a8b6d7","tid":1016784,"uid":182056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:39:57.000Z","msg":"自推，中到應一應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ea5517ae5b6ded235a77ef6351bb410f433574","tid":1016784,"uid":65253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d3ce668238d4a0de2f239603301129ecfb0ee8","tid":1016784,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:44:34.000Z","msg":"樓主有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b367b7edc9294b216593bf2dc9b3b6d7b6ce024","tid":1016784,"uid":107444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"1733fa0e74c70badaa76e2ff969c21e9f92ad70e","tid":1016784,"uid":214718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:14:32.000Z","msg":"獌連點睇"},{"pid":"29c1673ddc1ab1b2a1ac62db990c4ec922aa4cdd","tid":1016784,"uid":107444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:52:12.000Z","msg":"今晚？"},{"pid":"d6933354add26de037474c3f5e62fe914b332ed9","tid":1016784,"uid":182056,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"昨晚都係同樣理由買巴黎下盤，sorry 無時間出文。今日再睇！"},{"pid":"40494ecc9da8c2c3430969878fdc6423e089caf1","tid":1016784,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bc5689043182cf500d125197190eb66d8cb437","tid":1016784,"uid":95635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"犀利，今晚有無？"},{"pid":"2080f03144c9163a19d4e805d4cedbd5355e420e","tid":1016784,"uid":182056,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"睇過下第一場，聖伊天 對 斯特拉斯堡 ~ <br />\n<br />\n兩隊實力其實差唔多，積分只相差兩分，得失球客隊比主隊強得多，再睇埋近況客隊又好，近五場作客只輸俾榜首超晒班的巴黎兩球仲要係盃賽 (那場澳門係讓兩球，其實都無輸盤)；而主隊已四場不勝，只入四球失了十二球，咁既狀況客隊受讓半一，真係買得過!!!!! 咪住先，莊家唔係低能，呢 D 野個個都睇到，和都收晒會唔會咁好派錢先？我純以陰謀論睇莊家唔會咁好人，所以我今場會選擇聖伊天。<br />\n<br />\n我會買：小注試下主勝 @ 1.78，再少少地買埋佢 -1 @ 3.35"},{"pid":"9002b263c9d9c2bd9c1b93d7695b4d73374136d5","tid":1016784,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"跟一跟樓主"},{"pid":"bbac63589523664129aa34a967ffb90291c35e93","tid":1016784,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:36:39.000Z","msg":"2:0緊"},{"pid":"dae5ba06528943bb3811fb103d812ff93d1a385e","tid":1016784,"uid":182056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T19:32:01.000Z","msg":"場皇馬，澳到讓到半球高水，似乎今晚阿積士有計，馬會仲係平半低水仲未轉。往積管近況一面倒去晒皇馬到，唔通又送錢？"},{"pid":"3709d526829af9cffa71d9e7e7d4c26e228ca86b","tid":1016784,"uid":182056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci